        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Elaine M. Checketts Military Families Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to amend regulations to ensure that parental leave that has already been approved for a member of the Armed Forces who is a primary or secondary caregiver may not be terminated upon the death of the child for whom the leave was taken.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
